##########switching
tig view~m view-main~Show main view
tig view~d view-diff~Show diff view
tig view~l view-log~Show log view
tig view~L view-reflog~Show reflog view
tig view~t view-tree~Show tree view
tig view~f view-blob~Show blob view
tig view~b view-blame~Show blame view
tig view~r view-refs~Show refs view
tig view~s, S view-status~Show status view
tig view~c view-stage~Show stage view
rig view~y view-stash~Show stash view
tig view~g view-grep~Show grep view
tig view~p view-pager~Show pager view
tig view~h view-help~Show help view
##########Manipulation
tig view~<Enter>~Enter and open selected line
tig view~<~Go back to the previous view state
tig view~<Down>,<Ctrl-N>~Move to next
tig view~<Up>,<Ctrl-P>~Move to previous
tig view~,parent~Move to parent
tig view~<Tab>~Move focus to the next view
tig view~R,<F5>~Reload and refresh view
tig view~O~Maximize the current view
tig view~q~Close the current view
tig view~Q,<Ctrl-C>~Close all views and quit
#########Cursor navigation
tig movement~k~Move cursor one line up
tig movement~j~Move cursor one line down
tig movement~<PageDown>,<Space>~Move cursor one page down
tig movement~<PageUp>~Move cursor half a page up
tig movement~<Ctrl-D>~Move cursor half a page down
tig movement~<Ctrl-U>~Move cursor one page up
tig movement~<Home>~Move cursor to first line
tig movement~<End>~Move cursor to last line
##########Scrolling
tig movement~<Insert>,<Ctrl-Y>~Scroll one line up
tig movement~<Delete>,<Ctrl-E>~Scroll one line down
tig movement~<ScrollBack>~Scroll one page up
tig movement~<ScrollFwd>~Scroll one page down
tig movement~|~Scroll to the first line columns
tig movement~<Left>~ Scroll two columns left
tig movement~<Right>~Scroll two columns right
##########Searching
tig searh~/~Search the view
tig searh~?~Search backwards in the view
tig searh~n~Find next search match
tig searh~N~Find previous search match
##########More Searching
tig search~<Down>,<Ctrl-N>,<Ctrl-J>~Find next search match
tig search~<Up>,<Ctrl-P>,<Ctrl-K>~Find previous search match
##########Misc
tig misc~e~Open in editor
tig misc~:~Open the prompt
tig misc~o~Open the options menu
tig misc~<Ctrl-L>~Redraw the screen
tig misc~z~Stop all loading views
tig misc~v~Show version information
##########Option toggling
tig options~I~:toggle sort-order
tig options~i~:toggle sort-field
tig options~#~:toggle line-number
tig options~D~:toggle date
tig options~A~:toggle author
tig optionsi~Tilde~:toggle line-graphics
tig options~F~:toggle file-name
tig options~W~:toggle ignore-space
tig options~X~:toggle id
tig options~$~:toggle commit-title-overflow
tig options~%~:toggle file-filter
##########External commands:
tig more~C~!git commit -v
tig more~[-]~search bindings
##########Main
##########Option toggling
tig main~G~:toggle commit-title-graph
tig main~F~:toggle commit-title-refs
##########View-specific actions
tig main~u~Stage/unstage chunk or file changes
tig main~!~Revert chunk or file changes
tig main~M~Merge file using external tool
##########View-specific actions
tig main~u~Stage/unstage chunk or file changes
tig main~!~Revert chunk or file changes
tig main~1~Stage/unstage single line
tig main~\~Split current diff chunk
##########Option toggling:
tig main~[~:toggle diff-context -1
tig main~]~:toggle diff-context +1

